{{Infobox pageant titleholder
|name = Helen Prest-Ajayi
| title=Miss Nigeria 1979
| occupation= lawyer, businesswoman
| education =[[International School Ibadan]]<br/>[[Obafemi Awolowo University]]<br/>
[[King's College London]]
|birth_date={{Birth date and age|df=yes|1960|09|17}}
