'''Sara Tommasi''' (born 9 June 1981) is an [[Italy|Italian]] actress and television personality. She made her film debut in the 2008 comedy ''Ultimi della classe'' playing a teacher who had appeared in a "sexy" calendar shoot. Tommasi herself had appeared topless in a Max Calendar shoot in 2007. In 2010 she appeared nude in an episode of the television series ''[[Crimini (television series)|Crimini]]''.<ref>[http://www.repubblica.it/2008/05/sezioni/spettacoli_e_cultura/prof-tommasi/prof-tommasi/prof-tommasi.html Sara Tommasi, sexy supplente sulle orme della Fenech anni '70] (Italian)</ref><ref>[http://www.italianosdargentina.com.ar/index.php?IdNot=32533 Sara Tommasi, scandalo in Tv. La showgirl nuda per "Crimini"] (Italian)</ref><ref>[http://www.corriere.it/Primo_Piano/Spettacoli/2006/10_Ottobre/02/calendario.shtml Sara Tommasi, dalla Bocconi al calendario] (Italian)</ref><ref>[http://www.mymovies.it/biografia/?a=118963 Sara Tommasi biografia] (Italian)</ref>

She has dated footballers [[Mario Balotelli]] and [[Ronaldinho]]. She was an attendee at former prime minister [[Silvio Berlusconi]]'s private parties.<ref>"[http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/sport/football/3969535/Man-City-news-Mario-Balottelis-ex-girlfriend-in-protest-strip.html Mario Balotelli's ex in protest strip] ''The Sun'', 6 June 2012</ref><ref>[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2038055/Silvio-Berlusconi-recruited-harem-models-actresses-bunga-bunga-parties.html Berlusconi's 'harem' named] ''The Daily Mail'', 16 September 2011</ref>

==Adult Film==
Tommasi's first [[Hardcore pornography|hardcore]] film, ''Sara Tommasi: Il Mio Primo Film Hard'', featuring her in explicit, non-simulated sex scenes, was released in 2012.<ref>"[http://www.agoravox.it/Intervista-a-Sara-Tommasi-Il-porno.html Intervista a Sara Tommasi: "Il porno non è una novità] (Italian)</ref>

