[[File:Serge Kanyinda at JCC 2018.jpg|thumb|Serge Kanyinda at the [[Carthage Film Festival]] 2018]]
'''Serge Kanyinda''' is an actor from the [[Democratic Republic of the Congo]], best known for his performance as Magicien in the 2012 film ''[[War Witch]] (Rebelle)''.<ref>"Rebelle director Kim Nguyen learned of Congo’s filming hazards the hard way". ''[[Vancouver Sun]]'', October 18, 2012.</ref> He has [[albinism]].<ref>[http://filmmakermagazine.com/45800-kim-nguyen-on-war-witch/ "Director Kim Nguyen on War Witch"]. ''Filmmaker'', May 17, 2012.</ref>

Kanyinda won the [[Canadian Screen Award]] for [[Academy of Canadian Cinema and Television Award for Best Performance by an Actor in a Supporting Role|Best Supporting Actor]] at the [[1st Canadian Screen Awards]].<ref name=wattage>[https://www.thestar.com/entertainment/movies/2013/03/03/canadian_screen_awards_raises_the_star_wattage.html "Canadian Screen Awards raises the star wattage"]. ''[[Toronto Star]]'', March 3, 2013.</ref>

